<bibRefCitation id="EFDBA4A8FFA53C5FFE56BFAFFDEF8604" author="Bournier" box="[426,633,507,531]" firstAuthor="Bournier" page="357" pageId="3" pageNumber="241" pagination="357 - 366" refId="ref3162" refString="Bournier, A. (1993) Thysanopteres gallicoles de Nouvelle-Caledonie. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 98, 357 - 366. https: // doi. org / 10.3406 / bsef. 1993.17908" type="journal article" year="1993">Bournier, 1993: 357</bibRefCitation>
